"word":"fulfilling","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"thing","count":1},{"word":"legitimate","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"accidents","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"straight","count":1},{"word":"problem","count":1},{"word":"regarding","count":1},{"word":"incidents","count":1},{"word":"happened","count":1},{"word":"on-site","count":1},{"word":"engineer","count":1},{"word":"quick","count":1},{"word":"fix","count":1},{"word":"track","count":1},{"word":"injured","count":1},{"word":"working","count":1},{"word":"equipment","count":1},{"word":"jinzhou","count":1},{"word":"recovering","count":1},{"word":"left","count":1},{"word":"take","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"younger","count":1},{"word":"qualified","count":1},{"word":"whenever","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"wrong","count":1},{"word":"past","count":1},{"word":"front","count":1},{"word":"lines","count":1},{"word":"fixing","count":1},{"word":"coordinating","count":1},{"word":"repairs","count":1},{"word":"time","count":1},{"word":"shown","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"anywhere","count":1},{"word":"absence","count":1},{"word":"kinds","count":1},{"word":"difficulties","count":1},{"word":"dealing","count":1},{"word":"clues","count":1},{"word":"miners","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"around","count":1},{"word":"transport","count":1},{"word":"lorries","count":1},{"word":"sending","count":1},{"word":"check","count":1},{"word":"mean","count":1},{"word":"greater","count":1},{"word":"possibility","count":1},{"word":"communication","count":1},{"word":"returns","count":1},{"word":"normal","count":1},{"word":"temperature","count":1},{"word":"rising","count":1},{"word":"looks","count":1},{"word":"succeeded","count":1},{"word":"safely","count":1},{"word":"rebooting","count":1},{"word":"efforts","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Nope. Been everywhere he would show up. Didn't find him. Just like you.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Let's keep looking. We can't afford to have the Refinery Tower offline for too long.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"You should stop rushing before the guest even says anything. Let {Male=him;Female=her} finish.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Oh, a guest from the Ministry. Let me introduce myself. I'm the doctor of the Mine, Huayu.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The tall guy next to me is Lei'li, the foreman here, and this is Modee, a mineral expert from the Academy.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"A few days ago, I heard about the sample agreement between the Mine and the Ministry. Please, how should I address you?","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Ah, {PlayerName}, I see. But in the photo attached to the Ministry's request, the person in charge is a young, nervous-looking girl. How come...","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"I got the message and the photo from Uncle Hong, the senior officer-in-chief here. Look, this is the photo.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Hm, the ID is indeed from the Ministry of Development. Let's overlook the minor details, then. To be blunt, the Mine is facing some issues fulfilling the Ministry's request.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Haha, this thing is legitimate. Maybe there was some little accidents back at the Ministry. Now I'll be straight: the Mine is facing some problem too, regarding the Ministry's request.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Modee has more details.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Incidents like this have happened before, but our on-site engineer was always quick to fix it and get things back on track.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"But he injured himself a while back while working on some other equipment. He's in Jinzhou recovering now.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"That left Uncle Hong to take over. He used to be in charge of the Refinery Tower when he was younger, so he's more than qualified.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Whenever something went wrong in the past, Uncle Hong was always the one on the front lines, fixing things and coordinating repairs.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"But this time, Uncle Hong hasn't shown up, and we can't seem to find him anywhere in the Mine.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"With his absence, the Mine is having all kinds of difficulties dealing with the Refinery Tower.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Clues... The miners said they saw Uncle Hong around the transport lorries. We are sending more people to check if he's still there.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"More people mean greater possibility. Thank you.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"The communication returns normal, and the temperature is rising too. {PlayerName}, looks like you succeeded.","quest_name":"Shadows of the Past","quest_id":134000004},{"text":"Uncle Hong is safely back too. The Mine is rebooting the Refinery Tower. Thank you for your efforts!","quest_name":"Shadows of the Past","quest_id":134000004}]}